{"tid":1478064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解讀李嘉誠8月16號首次就逆權運動發表兩則廣告之含意","createTime":"2019-08-16T10:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T16:04:42.000Z","uid":226955,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67810b6d37288b20f09d6831ac8793ef8e7ed72b","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDb1q8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDb1q8J.jpg&h=a4497bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道今日香港首富李嘉誠出喺唔同報刊登咗兩個版本嘅廣告，等我地一齊解讀下當中嘅暗示啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先睇左邊第一個版本嘅文字：<br />\n<br />\n「最好的因<br />\n可成最壞的果<br />\n愛自由<br />\n愛中國<br />\n愛包容<br />\n愛香港<br />\n愛法治<br />\n愛自己」<br />\n<br />\n將每句最後一個字拎出嚟，就係：<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">因果由國容港治己</span>」八隻大字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />意思可以咁解讀，<span style=\"color: red;\">所有因果都皆係由你中國去造成嘅，容許香港管治返自己先係正途</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而右邊第二個版本嘅文字：<br />\n<br />\n「黃台之瓜，何堪再摘。」<br />\n<br />\n呢句引文源於武則天嘅太子李賢嘅遺言，當時武則天要處死李賢，李賢作咗呢首詩，<span style=\"color: red;\">暗示武則天以強權壓迫弱勢，希望作為母親嘅武則天唔好再殘害唐代宗室，唔好再殘害自己嘅仔女</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n套用返當今香港局勢，詩中控訴武則天作為一個母親，去逼害自己仔女，大家係咪有似塵相識嘅感覺？<span style=\"color: red;\">忽然回想起最近香港亦有某人自稱係母親，並以香港人比喻為自己仔女，此番廣告似乎意味深長。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奇怪之處亦出自呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既然中國五千年文化有咁多詩篇，憂國憂民嘅詩句多如星海，點解一定要引用武則天之子李賢嘅遺言呢？李嘉誠係咪意有所指呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難得望到誠哥對香港人語重心長嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞到我一時之間感激流涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不知所言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />還望各位多多見諒"},{"pid":"df8d2a4b24f275647c7a3c49edca8cf799d68a0b","tid":1478064,"uid":245362,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZaEXrX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZaEXrX.png&h=5d9c8e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XFxx0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XFxx0j.png&h=d8eb8b1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c383f6477568e8c7c096e1d4aab21a375f955b43","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"370f569511979d81ee1cd90f11198be4e5b348a9","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0096b8a2581775e17afce8d025e52f00fceb411e","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0486990fba0e876b92a60963203d575273f006ef","tid":1478064,"uid":40061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"我們於今日約下午2時已知悉以上資訊<br />\n多謝你的整合！"},{"pid":"a96c8a67f0ae523239871f0a3694a512d07fcdd4","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0486990fba0e876b92a60963203d575273f006ef","tid":1478064,"uid":40061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"我們於今日約下午2時已知悉以上資訊<br />\n多謝你的整合！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdae0d0801df937b7e8a565f1fab39b1bc628ec","tid":1478064,"uid":35084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96c8a67f0ae523239871f0a3694a512d07fcdd4","tid":1478064,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0486990fba0e876b92a60963203d575273f006ef","tid":1478064,"uid":40061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"我們於今日約下午2時已知悉以上資訊<br />\n多謝你的整合！"},